Changes made:
This repository contains a square-aspect vector-graphics inverse derived from
the IBM VGA 9x14 bitmap font. The source 9x14 forms were adapted to a wider
square-cell format based on a 14x14 grid per glyph, with changes to utility
glyphs where needed to support that wider format. The repository also includes
generated SVG font, TrueType font, and condensed BMP raster outputs at multiple
block sizes.

